#

Korean BBQ Beef Tacos with Spicy Slaw and Kimchi

$15.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

SoySesame

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

KoreanTacosFusionSpicy

Description

Savory Korean BBQ beef tucked into warm tortillas, topped with spicy slaw and tangy kimchi for a bold flavor burst!

Ingredients

  • Flank steak: 1 lb
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tbsp
  • Sesame oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Tortillas: 8
  • Cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • Carrot: 1 cup, julienned
  • Gochujang (Korean chili paste): 2 tbsp
  • Rice vinegar: 1 tbsp
  • Kimchi: 1 cup, for serving
  • Green onions: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp, for garnish
